        <head>Patience</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Patience</l>
          <l>Be patient, she said</l>
          <l>But how long,</l>
          <l>How long I ask</l>
          <l>How long will I wait?</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>You wrap me like a mother,</l>
          <l>The guard of my mind </l>
          <l>A delicate balance,</l>
          <l>Sickness and cure</l>
          <l>What's insane ,</l>
          <l> Sanity is what? </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>But I can't,</l>
          <l>I can't wait</l>
          <l>Be patient </l>
          <l>Patience, she said</l>
          <l>Well, I trust you.. </l>
          <l>And I love you…</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
